@Steven M.

Well I’m definitely not drunk and I thought it was one of the harder Tuesdays I can remember.
A lot of tricky clueing. Some of it was this seemed like a “young” puzzle, not just that I didn’t know the revealer, but stuff like Play Store purchase and Insta post which were gettable but just not instantly accessible to my brain. But still this was crunchy all over— I never thought I’d see “Dance performed  in Smetana’s ‘Battered Bride’” or “Residents of the Realm of Four Parts”  on a Tuesday. Not that I am complaining, I loved this puzzle and appreciate a harder Tuesday. Maybe the editors took to heart everyone complaining how easy puzzles have been lately.

